OL,7,FLeasehold flats will be banned under
OL,8,Fnew proposals detailed by the
OL,9,Fgovernment.
OL,11,FThe housing minister said the changes
OL,12,F"mark the beginning of the end" for
OL,13,Fthe "feudal" leasehold system, giving
OL,14,Fhomeowners greater control over their
OL,15,Fproperties under a new 'commonhold'
OL,16,Fsystem.
