OL,3,CLeasehold flats are being banned by
OL,4,Cthe government - what does it mean for
OL,5,Cyou?
OL,7,FThe Labour government made abolishing
OL,8,Fthe leasehold system a key manifesto
OL,9,Fpledge, and on Monday published more
OL,10,Fdetails of what will replace it.
OL,12,FWhat does 'commonhold' mean?
OL,14,FA commonhold system allows property
OL,15,Fowners to own and manage their
OL,16,Fbuildings together, rather than the
OL,17,Fultimate control being with a third-
OL,18,Fparty landlord.
