OL,5,Cyou?
OL,7,FMembers of the commonhold can then
OL,8,Fvote on decisions around building
OL,9,Fmaintenance and service charges.
OL,11,FThe government proposals put forward
OL,12,Fon Monday include strict rules on how
OL,13,Fcommonhold buildings can be managed,
OL,14,Fin order to reassure mortgage lenders
OL,15,Fthe buildings won't be neglected.
OL,17,FThe plans also allow people in
OL,18,Fcommonhold buildings to separate them
OL,19,Finto different sections, meaning
OL,20,Fpeople would only pay for and run the
OL,21,Famenities that benefit them.
