OL,3,CLeasehold flats are being banned by
OL,4,Cthe government - what does it mean for
OL,5,Cyou?
OL,7,FIn 2024 only 0.01% of housing stock in
OL,8,Fthe UK was commonhold properties,
OL,9,Fmaking it an exception to the rest of
OL,10,Fthe world, where commonhold systems
OL,11,Fare much more prevalent.
OL,13,FHasn't this been promised before?
OL,15,FThe previous Conservative government
OL,16,Falso promised reform to the leasehold
OL,17,Fsystem - Sajid Javid said he'd ban new-
OL,18,Fbuild houses being sold as leasehold
OL,19,Fin 2017, and in 2021 Michael Gove
OL,20,Fpledged to abolish the system entirely.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
