OL,7,FBut Gove's plans were watered down
OL,8,Fafter a battle with Downing Street,
OL,9,Fmeaning a total ban was kicked into
OL,10,Fthe long grass.
OL,12,FOther reforms were implemented - in
OL,13,F2022 the Leasehold Reform (Ground
OL,14,FRent) Act ended ground rent for most
OL,15,Fnew long residential leases.
OL,17,FBut many of the reforms promised by
OL,18,Fthe Conservatives never came into
OL,19,Feffect, and have been absorbed into
OL,20,FLabour's plans for the Leasehold and
OL,21,FCommonhold Reform Bill.
